Who we are
Whether you’re on the hunt for that perfect piece of furniture, looking for vintage clothes, or out for the best local coffee or craft beer, you can find it at Sidecar!
Owned by couple Jessie Ritz and Derek Ridgway, Sidecar started out as an idea for a place where people could get together. Jessie had a natural eye for eclectic styles and Derek possessing unique talents in all things hands on- it was a natural next step for them to start a business together.
While in many different forms, Sidecar has been around for years and for the last six years has made its permanent home on New York and Woodland Blvd.
